description: A residential-led redevelopment comprising the erection of five buildings ranging from 3-9 storeys, plus a podium level, for the provision of 147 residential units and 191sqm (GIA) non-residential floor space (Use Class E (a, b, c, d, g) / F1 / F2), installation of plant, public realm, car parking, landscaping and highway works and other associated works (This application site is within the setting of a Grade II Listed Building: Chapel of St George and St Helena)
